---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="LongLore helps you learn Chinese through compelling historical stories, with sentence-by-sentence translations, pinyin, and spaced repetition.">
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>About LongLore 龙知</h1>

    <p>
      LongLore helps people learn Chinese through compelling historical stories.
      Instead of boring textbook dialogues, we use real stories from Chinese
      history — the Grand Canal, the Mandate of Heaven, the Three Kingdoms, and
      more.
    </p>
    <p>
      Each story comes with sentence-by-sentence translations, pinyin
      pronunciation guides, and vocabulary glosses. Our spaced repetition system
      ensures you actually remember what you learn.
    </p>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>
      Learning with LongLore follows a simple cycle:
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <strong>Read</strong> — Immerse yourself in a story from Chinese history.
        Tap any sentence for its translation, pinyin, and word-by-word glosses.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Discover</strong> — Save new words to your personal vocabulary as
        you encounter them naturally in context.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Remember</strong> — Our spaced repetition system schedules
        reviews at the optimal time so new words move into long-term memory.
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      We believe learning should be interesting, not tedious. Textbooks fill
      pages with contrived dialogues about buying train tickets. We'd rather you
      read about Zhuge Liang's strategies or the construction of the Great Wall.
    </p>
    <p>
      Real content. Real history. Real Chinese. That's the LongLore way.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  .prose h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display-en);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .prose ul,
  .prose ol {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-jade);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
